{"tid":1632253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎屌我p牌左膠]做個醒目裝修師 四色分類你要知","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:57:33.000Z","uid":267351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"015453f8a6c20af9c2db0bab69be71a450ff4ca8","tid":1632253,"uid":267351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"見連登互屌足成晚好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一直打到依家就係靠和勇一家不互屌不割𥱊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔係有共識要四色分類架咩?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLuNw1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLuNw1y.jpg&h=12fb977e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm2n5hY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm2n5hY.jpg&h=2cc9bc99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[black]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑裝修</span>[/black]<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅裝飾</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藍罷買</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃幫襯</span></span><br />\n有群眾共識就要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一齊堅守</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔洗下下硬裝修嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下下都用劍你估我地係藍絲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裝修完要即時有文宣隊洗下地等記者朋友連埋文宣一齊影番張靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔離po好多文宣巴整左靚旗仔大家都要用下架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣追唔切<br />\n和理非好似大笨象咁都要俾啲時間佢地進化<br />\n真係有和理非唔明點解咁多裝修架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求勇武都俾啲時間同耐性個社會去明白同接受我地做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌我好愛你地每一個大家一直努力頂住好冇呀</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f40ff182f74891ddd8a1229244c104c8ee45195c","tid":1632253,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"呢個共識今日完全做唔到"},{"pid":"984abf18c88484fe11361fcfd019bb1894f87f97","tid":1632253,"uid":267351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"90b045654161ff49e710f4d9f0572987c52e4936","tid":1632253,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n希望大家推番岩方向"},{"pid":"f64f1b99b2f6a062988fe5cef64fd743770b5a6a","tid":1632253,"uid":267351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:14.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f84b174f708c811a0818b8a1db5255b406548f54","tid":1632253,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"0d454fd5b9928d46f5900015127305ccb1805b25","tid":1632253,"uid":267351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4742e0aac7438a65044ba8f9888915e6de129b44","tid":1632253,"uid":267351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:03.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"611ed20fff2b79d8242d6a9c3e0fbde62a48e6ba","tid":1632253,"uid":267351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"5ec9d9a39b68b6829454329c0c4b3060897b43d3","tid":1632253,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01d382d11c78f2cdd379ccae7c56f961d3a472